::Killfest::

Killfest looks at Speedbreaker for a moment and then nods. He jumps 
in, sitting down at the seat and aiming his missile launcher at Angel 
Prime. He fires one missile, watching it lock on and head for the 
Maximal.

"How fast can you go?" he asks Speedbreaker as he aims another 
missile.
